OL,5, The government is poised to step in to 
OL,6, tackle the gas price crisis and carbon 
OL,7, dioxide shortage, Business Secretary   
OL,8, Kwasi Kwarteng has said.               
OL,10,FThe move comes as rising wholesale gas 
OL,11,Fcosts are forcing smaller providers out
OL,12,Fof business.                           
OL,14,FMr Kwarteng told the BBC that lending  
OL,15,Fmoney to bigger firms to help them take
OL,16,Fon stranded customers was an option.   
OL,18,FHe also said the government could      
OL,19,Fsubsidise the country's biggest carbon 
OL,20,Fdioxide producer to bolster supplies.  
